Package com.intel.icecp.cli.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecuteCommand
    This class calls RpcClient to execute commands.
    LatestCommand
    Retrieve the latest bytes from the given channel.
    ModuleLoadCommand  
    PublishCommand
    Publish a stream of bytes as a message on the given channel URI
    ReadAttributeCommand
    Read a remote attribute and print the result to STDOUT
    ReadAttributeCommand.Builder
    Builder pattern: use this to correctly assemble the data required for a ReadAttributeCommand.
    SubscribeCommand
    Print messages received on the subscribed channel (one on each line).
    SubscribeCommand.Builder
    Builder pattern: use this to correctly assemble the data required for a ReadAttributeCommand.
    VersionCommand
    Print the current version of the tool; note that this command relies on the maven-jar-plugin and its manifest properties addDefaultImplementationEntries and addDefaultSpecificationEntries.
    WriteAttributeCommand  
    WriteAttributeCommand.Builder
    Builder pattern: use this to correctly assemble the data required for a WriteAttributeCommand.
